  "translations": {
    "en": "Muhammad ibn al-Hasan ibn Ahmad ibn al-Walid (may God have mercy on him) narrated to us. He said: Muhammad ibn Yahya al-Attar narrated to us, from Muhammad ibn al-Husayn ibn Abi al-Khattab, from Ibn Abi Najran, from al-Muthanna, from Muhammad ibn Muslim. He said:",
    "ur": "محمد بن الحسن بن احمد بن الولید (رحمہ اللہ) نے ہم سے بیان کیا۔ انہوں نے کہا:",
    "tr": "Muhammed b. el-Hasen b. Ahmed b. el-Velid (r.a.) bize rivayet etti. Dedi ki: Muhammed b. Yahya el-Attar, Muhammed b. el-Hüseyin b. Ebu'l-Hattab'dan, İbn Ebi Necran'dan, el-Müsenna'dan, Muhammed b. Müslim'den bize rivayet etti. Dedi ki:",
    "fa": "محمد بن الحسن بن احمد بن الولید (رحمه الله) برایمان روایت کرد. گفت:",
    "id": "Muhammad bin al-Hasan bin Ahmad bin al-Walid (semoga Allah merahmatinya) menceritakan kepada kami. Dia berkata:",
    "bn": "মুহাম্মাদ ইবনে আল-হাসান আমাদের কাছে বর্ণনা করেছেন। তিনি বলেছেন:",
    "es": "Muhammad ibn al-Hasan ibn Ahmad ibn al-Walid (que Dios tenga piedad de él) nos narró. Dijo:",
    "fr": "Muhammad ibn al-Hasan ibn Ahmad ibn al-Walid (que Dieu lui fasse miséricorde) nous a rapporté. Il a dit :",
    "de": "Muhammad ibn al-Hasan ibn Ahmad ibn al-Walid (möge Gott sich seiner erbarmen) berichtete uns. Er sagte:",
    "ru": "Мухаммад ибн аль-Хасан рассказал нам. Он сказал:",
    "zh": "穆罕默德·本·哈桑·本·艾哈迈德·本·瓦利德（愿安拉慈悯他）向我们讲述了。他说："
  }
}